8月26日，[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]中部形成了一股热带低气压<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="HURDAT" />。系统向西飘流数日，到8月30日时已经增强成热带风暴并略朝西南方向转向，再于此后不久达到最高强度，属弱热带风暴标准<ref name="HURDAT" />。8月31日，风暴从[[格兰德河|格兰德河]]河口附近上岸<ref name="MWR" />，并在陆上行进期间减弱<ref name="HURDAT" />。多个沿海地区收到公告，之后[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]海岸受到狂风和大浪和冲击。[[布朗斯维尔_(得克萨斯州)|布朗斯维尔]]遭受了一定程度的财产损失<ref name="MWR" />。大风掀开了[[卡梅倫縣_(德克薩斯州)|卡梅倫縣]][[伊莎贝尔港_(德克萨斯州)|伊莎贝尔港]]多所房屋的屋顶，还摧毁了一些[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]居民的木屋。风暴还将渔船吹至搁浅，幸运的是没有造成人员丧生<ref>{{cite news | title = Shores of Texas Swept by Fierce Gulf Storm | date = 1910-08-31 | publisher = ''The Herald-Journal'' | accessdate = 2015-02-06 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=wEwsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=z8kEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3029,3111758&dq=storm+texas&hl=en | language = en | archive-date = 2020-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200719034740/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=wEwsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=z8kEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3029,3111758&dq=storm+texas&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。不过，有两个小镇与布朗斯维尔之间的通讯中断<ref>{{cite news |title=Gulf Storm Increases; Government Launch May Be Lost -- Coast Points Are Cut Off. |date=1910-08-31 |publisher=''The New York Times'' |accessdate=2015-02-06 |archivedate=2012-11-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109235839/http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?_r=1&res=9805E1D91239E433A25752C3A96E9C946196D6CF |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |url=http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?_r=1&res=9805E1D91239E433A25752C3A96E9C946196D6CF |language=en }}</ref>。
